Class DOMEventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.dom.events.DOMEventType

  • public final class DOMEventType
extends java.lang.Object
    The list of supported HTML event types.
    受支持的HTML事件类型的列表。

      • OnLoad

        public static final DOMEventType OnLoad
        Fires when the user agent finishes loading all content within a document, including window, frames, objects and images. For elements, it fires when the target element and all of its content has finished loading.
        用户代理完成文档中所有内容的加载（包括窗口，框架，对象和图像）时触发。对于元素，当目标元素及其所有内容完成加载时触发。

      • OnUnload

        public static final DOMEventType OnUnload
        Fires when the user agent removes all content from a window or frame. For elements, it fires when the target element or any of its content has been removed.
        当用户代理从窗口或框架中删除所有内容时触发。对于元素，当目标元素或其任何内容被删除时，它将触发。
